'''Glowvines''' were phosphorescent [[Plant/Legends|plants]] that grew on [[Haruun Kal/Legends|Haruun Kal]]. They glowed in several different [[Color/Legends|colors]], and the [[Korun/Legends|Korunnai]] used them for night vision.

